-- Select relevant information for objects classified as SN II with specified conditions
WITH sn_ii_objects AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          p.oid,
          p.class_name,
          p.probability,
          p.ranking
   FROM OBJECT o
   JOIN probability p ON o.oid = p.oid
   WHERE p.class_name = 'SNII'
     AND p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND p.probability > 0.6
     AND p.ranking = 1
     AND o.firstmjd BETWEEN 2458600 AND 2459580 -- Corresponds roughly to 2019-2022
),
     sn_ii_candidates AS
  (SELECT d.candid,
          d.oid,
          d.mjd,
          d.ra,
          d.dec,
          d.magpsf,
          d.sigmapsf,
          d.fid
   FROM detection d
   JOIN sn_ii_objects s ON d.oid = s.oid
   WHERE d.mjd BETWEEN 2458600 AND 2459580 ),
     mag_stats AS
  (SELECT ms.oid,
          ms.fid,
          ms.magmax,
          ms.magmax_corr,
          ms.dm_first,
          ms.dmdt_first
   FROM magstat ms
   WHERE ms.oid IN
       (SELECT oid
        FROM sn_ii_objects) ),
     rise_rates AS
  (SELECT s.oid, -- Calculate initial rise rate as mag change over time in days
 CASE
     WHEN COUNT(*) > 1 THEN (MAX(ms.magmax) - MIN(ms.magmax)) / NULLIF(MAX(d.mjd) - MIN(d.mjd), 0)
     ELSE NULL
 END AS initial_rise_rate
   FROM sn_ii_candidates d
   JOIN magstat ms ON d.oid = ms.oid
   WHERE ms.fid IN (1,
                    2) -- g and r bands

   GROUP BY s.oid),
     detection_counts AS
  (SELECT oid,
          COUNT(*) AS ndet
   FROM detection
   GROUP BY oid)
SELECT o.oid,
       c.candid,
       m.magmax,
       m.sigmapsf,
       m.dm_first,
       c.fid
FROM sn_ii_objects o
JOIN sn_ii_candidates c ON o.oid = c.oid
JOIN magstat m ON o.oid = m.oid
AND m.fid = c.fid
JOIN rise_rates r ON o.oid = r.oid
JOIN detection_counts d ON o.oid = d.oid
WHERE r.initial_rise_rate > 0.5
  AND d.ndet > 50
  AND c.mjd BETWEEN 2458600 AND 2459580;

  detection.candid, detection.fid as f_id,detection.magpsf, detection.sigmapsf_corr, detection.sigmapsf_corr_ext

    AND probability.probability > 0.6
    AND object.ndet > 50

WHERE
  magstat.dmdt_first < -0.5
  AND (magstat.fid = 1 OR magstat.fid = 2)
) AS sq

  ON sq.oid = detection.oid
WHERE
